{"tid":991294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今次全民派錢搞出咁多問題，主要問題係咪因為要減嚟減去所致？","createTime":"2019-01-22T09:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T16:56:37.000Z","uid":64694,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d19b033b5ca987e36ea2a7d32446f908f87279","tid":991294,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"其實如果原本唔使減嚟減去，係咪可以就噉去銀行show身份證，登記身份證，之後銀行拎四張一千蚊（或者八張五百蚊）出嚟，處理一個人係咪都唔使1分鐘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係而家因為要減嚟減去，所以又要填表又剩，而且減完之後個數好唔整齊，可能會出現小數，例如3456.7噉樣，個數太散，而且每個人個數都唔同，好難準備唔同嘅紙幣同散銀，所以唔可以就噉拎現金，變成一定要銀行戶口過數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以最後件事就搞成噉，話要咩三億行政費，其實陳茂波係因為聽咗上次派六千蚊嗰陣誠哥話我唔需要嗰六千蚊，所以有噉嘅打算？但係我一直都唔明，覺得冇需要唔攞咪得囉，講噉多嘢做乜呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c8b4434da73858f084ed1aeb57609eb4160f9e","tid":991294,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"上面漏咗個$，$3456.7"},{"pid":"e91b9ab0bfcff3e31b1ac677ecbd145d226ed176","tid":991294,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2f56676057b0e5954a0f19ad897f86add6f747","tid":991294,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/171717/thumbnail/30c6d8c7f89e9f850b510417f568f7ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F171717%2Fthumbnail%2F30c6d8c7f89e9f850b510417f568f7ee.jpg&h=df979db3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"370f51df3509ce2861aa3da8828b1d7c2bbaef58","tid":991294,"uid":200328,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:22:49.000Z","msg":"搞咁多野慳埋啲差額蝕返係行政費到, 贏粒糖輸間廠<br />\n再蝕埋剩餘可憐既果少少民望<br />\n盤數計到成pat屎咁<br />\n咁既人做財爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo